     C*****************************************************************
     C*
     C** Parameter list for current program invocation.
     C*
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           W0RTN
     C                     PARM           W0CMT   3
     C*
     C** Set up subroutine stack name
     C*
     C                     ADD  1         Q
     C                     MOVEL'MAIN'    @STK,Q
     C*
     C**  Initial processing - Once Only
     C*
     C           ##INIT    IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     EXSR SRINIT
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       ##INIT  1
     C                     END
     C*
     C** Initialisation processing
     C*
     C                     EXSR SRINZ
     C*
     C** Main processing
     C*
     C                     EXSR SRMAIN
     C*
     C** Audit Processing
     C*
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
     C*
     C** Unwind subroutine stack name
     C*
