     C/EJECT
     C*****************************************************************
     C* Subroutine  :  SRMAIN                                         *
     C* Function    :  Main processing                                *
     C*                                                               *
     C* Called by   :  Mainline                                       *
     C* Calls       :  CG6055 - Lending Past Due Notices              *
     C*****************************************************************
     C           SRMAIN    BEGSR
     C*
     C** Set up subroutine stack name
     C*
     C                     ADD  1         Q       50
     C                     MOVEL'SRMAIN'  @STK,Q
     C*
     C** Read through PSTCU
     C*
     C                     READ PSTCU                    50
     C*
     C** Read until End of File
     C*
     C                     MOVE *OFF      *IN30
     C           PPDU      IFEQ 0
     C           INPD      ANDEQ0
     C                     MOVE *ON       *IN30
     C                     ENDIF
     C*
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ'0'                        B1
     C*
     C** If Confirmation Requested and Past Due amounts not nil,
     C*
     C           PDRQ      IFEQ 'Y'
     C           *IN30     ANDEQ*OFF
     C/COPY WNCPYSRC,CG6050C004
     C*
     C** Increment the count of PSTCU records read
     C*
     C                     ADD  1         ##DREC  50
     C/COPY WNCPYSRC,CG6050C001
     C*
     C** Call CG6055, Lending Past Due Notices
     C*
     C                     CALL 'CG6055'
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   ##RTCD  7
     C                     PARM W0CMT     ##CMT   3
     C                     PARM           ##COPD  1
     C                     PARM           DSPARM
     C*
     C** Error in called program.
     C*
     C           ##RTCD    IFNE *BLANK                     B3
     C*
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT
     C*
     C** Database error
     C*
     C                     MOVEL'CG6055  'W0FILE           ***************
     C                     MOVEL##RTCD    W0KEY            * DB ERROR 01 *
     C                     Z-ADD01        W0ERNB           ***************
     C                     MOVEL'MEM5003' W0MSGD
     C                     MOVEL'MIDAS  ' W0MSGF
     C                     EXSR SRERR
     C                     END                             E3
     C*                                                                   CLE172
     C** Call CG6055LE, Lending Past Due Notices                          CLE172
     C*                                                                   CLE172
     C           CLE172    IFEQ 'Y'                                       CLE172
     C                     CALL 'CG6055LE'                                CLE172
     C                     PARM *BLANKS   ##RTCD  7                       CLE172
     C                     PARM W0CMT     ##CMT   3                       CLE172
     C                     PARM           ##COPD  1                       CLE172
     C                     PARM           DSPARM                          CLE172
     C*                                                                   CLE172
     C** Error in called program.                                         CLE172
     C*                                                                   CLE172
     C           ##RTCD    IFNE *BLANK                     B3             CLE172
     C*                                                                   CLE172
     C                     EXSR SRAUDT                                    CLE172
     C*                                                                   CLE172
     C** Database error                                                   CLE172
     C*                                                                   CLE172
     C                     MOVEL'CG6055LE'W0FILE           ***************CLE172
     C                     MOVEL##RTCD    W0KEY            * DB ERROR 01 *CLE172
     C                     Z-ADD01        W0ERNB           ***************CLE172
     C                     MOVEL'MEM5003' W0MSGD                          CLE172
     C                     MOVEL'MIDAS  ' W0MSGF                          CLE172
     C                     EXSR SRERR                                     CLE172
     C                     END                             E3             CLE172
     C                     ENDIF                                          CLE172
     C*
     C** If past due notices are produced by CG6055, set the past due
     C** notices indicator on PSTCU to 'N'
     C*
     C/COPY WNCPYSRC,CG6050C002
     C           ##COPD    IFEQ 'Y'                        B3
     C                     MOVEL'N'       PDRQ
     C                     UPDATPDUEDUF
     C                     END                             E3
     C*
     C                     END                             E2
     C*
     C** Commit
     C*
     C                     COMIT
     C*
     C                     READ PSTCU                    50
     C*
     C                     END                             E1
     C*
     C           EXMAIN    TAG
     C*
     C** Unwind subroutine stack name
     C*
     C                     MOVEA*BLANKS   @STK,Q
     C                     SUB  1         Q
     C*
     C                     ENDSR
